# Roadmap

## Phase 1 (Current)
- Core runtime: registry + install store + runner
- Workspace app manager
- Admin control center
- Local storage installs per workspace

## Phase 2
- Modules with manifests (auto-merged registry)
- Widgets registry + widget placements
- Optional: Persist installs to Firestore
- Tier enforcement (read-only rules first)

## Phase 3
- Stripe integration for paid modules/apps/widgets
- Team workspaces + role-based access
- Audit logs + activity stream

## Phase 4
- Marketplace improvements (search, categories, featured modules)
- Module versioning / updates
- Export/import workspace configuration

